divs: Sighting DetailsOn July 5th, My famitly and I were sitting out side. When we noticed something floating in the sky. I would not really say it was floating, it was just sitting there for about 15-20 minutes. Then it just went up in to the clouds. It looked kind of like a person. But not real sure. That is the only time we have seen it. I did take 3 pics of it. The are pretty good pics.
